parameters: ...Hmm... I wonder if it's just my imagination...

I felt like someone was here... but when I entered, the
atmosphere in the room was cold.

I watched as the room gradually became chilly, and while
thinking that it might be time to take out the kotatsu,
I sank deeply into the sofa.

Even if I change the channel, there isn't anything
particularly interesting on.
There's no program that seems as interesting as the news.

When I was absentmindedly watching TV, sleepiness suddenly
attacked me.
I can feel the flickering light of the fluorescent lamp.

I can hear the sound of an old fluorescent lamp
flickering on and off near my ear, as if it's coming
from a distance.
Senpai, that's not good. If you fall asleep on the sofa...
You might catch a cold, you know?
Renka is on top of me.
Fluttering wings and a strangely moving slender tail.
Ah, is this a dream? I closed my eyes again.

At that moment, warm breath entered my ears, and my
runaway spirit hurriedly returned to reality.
Hehe... It's not a dream, you know.
Would you prefer it to be a dream?

I couldn't resist your energy, senpai, it was too
delicious, so I had to go home
Even your silly expression is cute.
It's not a compliment, you know...
Ugh, I know, that kind of thing.
However... when I say it was delicious... I'm serious, you know?
Oh my... You don't seem to be feeling well.

Renka gently explores my crotch from below with her slender
fingers over my clothes.

I was repulsed by that sensation, but at the same time,
I was incredibly excited.
It has become delicious~ Well then, let's dig in.

My thing, which is inserted without any foreplay, quickly
flips the panties.
The feeling of something slipping out.

I ejaculated prematurely just from feeling Renka's
uterus a few times.
Hehe, it's fine, senpai. Please give me more
Her slender tail is swaying gently, looking pleasurable.
My hips move naturally, without my own will.
All I can do is breathe roughly as much as I can.

The night is deep and sticky, making me not want to wake
up...
D Ending... Recommended by the Semen Sommelier.
